statements.sql: select sonum,refnum,shipmark,ifnull((sum(TotalAssgn)/sum(totalAll)) * 100,0) as percent from (select `solist`.`sonum`, refnum,shipmark,if(moresolist.sonum is not null,1 ,0) as totalAll,if(moresolist.sonum is not null and asgnto is not null and asgnto !="",1 ,0) as TotalAssgn from `solist` left join `moresolist` on solist.sonum COLLATE  utf8_general_ci = moresolist.sonum AND moresolist.trxstatus in ("A","C") where solist.trxstatus IN ("A","C")) as sub  group by `sonum` order by `sonum` desc

select `sonum`, refnum,shipmark,ifnull((sum(TotalAssgn)/sum(totalAll)) * 100,0) as percent from (select `solist`.`sonum`, refnum,shipmark,if(moresolist.sonum is not null,1 ,0) as totalAll,if(moresolist.sonum is not null and asgnto is not null and asgnto !="",1 ,0) as TotalAssgn from `solist` left join `moresolist` on solist.sonum COLLATE  utf8_general_ci = moresolist.sonum AND moresolist.trxstatus in ("A","C") where solist.trxstatus IN ("A","C")) as sub  group by `sub`.`sonum` having percent < 100 order by `sonum` desc limit 6 offset 0

select sonum,refnum,shipmark,ifnull((sum(TotalAssgn)/sum(totalAll)) * 100,0) as percent from (select `solist`.`sonum`, refnum,shipmark,if(moresolist.sonum is not null,1 ,0) as totalAll,if(moresolist.sonum is not null and asgnto is not null and asgnto !="",1 ,0) as TotalAssgn from `solist` left join `moresolist` on solist.sonum COLLATE  utf8_general_ci = moresolist.sonum AND moresolist.trxstatus in ("A","C") where solist.trxstatus IN ("A","C")) as sub  group by `sonum` having percent = 100 order by `sonum` desc limit 6 offset 0
